# IMPORTANT: Never commit appsettings with real secrets.
# Use environment variables or a secrets manager (Azure Key Vault, AWS Secrets
# Manager, HashiCorp Vault) for:
#   - ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection (SA password)
#   - Jwt__Key
#   - ExternalProviders__WebhookSecret
# The appsettings.json files in this repo contain DEVELOPMENT DEFAULTS ONLY.
# appsettings.Production.json must not contain secrets.

